                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390513-1660-offence-1 t18390513-cd-167"></join>14th of May</rs>, 13 shillings and 6 sixpences, the monies of <persName id="t18390513-name-1095" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-1095" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-1095" type="surname" value="SAMPSON"></interp>
